 2019-04892019-05-09,  ,  ,  GAC, 
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing to sign, execute and issue and Instrument of Full Powers, subject to ratification, the Headquarters Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Organization
PrecisOrder Authorizing (a) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the HEADQUARTERS AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE NORTHWEST ATLANTIC FISHERIES ORGANIZATION; or (b) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the HEADQUARTERS AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE NORTHWEST ATLANTIC FISHERIES ORGANIZATION.
